Subject: winealsa: re-subscribe MIDI devices when they reappear
 on the sequencer

Subscribe the shared input port to the system announce port; on SND_SEQ_EVENT_PORT_START re-match
the new port by its winmm display name, adopt the new address, and re-subscribe any open input/output.
---
 dlls/winealsa.drv/alsamidi.c | 133 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-----
 1 file changed, 115 insertions(+), 18 deletions(-)

